data.text: Prime opportunity in the heart of Dodge county, where 21 sprawling acres of pristine, tillable, land await your vision. Currently farmed for agricultural use, however, the township has it slated for commercial/industrial use. Perfect location for warehouse or storage units alike. This expansive parcel boasts fertile soil, no wetlands and presents a canvas for countless possibilities. Positioned strategically, this property offers the versatility of being potentially rezoned for light industrial use, making it an ideal prospect for investors seeking to capitalize on the burgeoning demand for storage facilities in the area.Nestled amidst serene surroundings, yet conveniently accessible from major transportation routes.
